QuestData.Title: Growing in Power
QuestData.Description:
Wonderful news, $n!
You have gathered enough Anima. The Queen is now able to empower the Heart of the Forest!
QuestData.LogDescription: Witness the Winter Queen empower the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: We're on the right track, $n! Keep doing what you're doing and it will be back to its full, glorious, starryness in no time!
